 []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Why are atheists such feckless cowards .\", \"from\": 18591, \"to\": 18632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \".\", \"from\": 18633, \"to\": 18634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \".\\\"\", \"from\": 18635, \"to\": 18637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pretty sure that *this* atheist recently wrote numerous, full-throated condemnations of the nihilists mocking Christian values.\", \"from\": 18639, \"to\": 18766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18749, \"end\": 18765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999944968009454, \"rank\": 5.501235583142923e-06, \"text\": \"Christian values\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sam wrote:Pretty sure that *this* atheist recently wrote numerous, full-throated condemnations of the nihilists mocking Christian values.\", \"from\": 18768, \"to\": 18905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18768, \"end\": 18771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9954456802727973, \"rank\": 0.00438032272570914, \"text\": \"Sam\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 18888, \"end\": 18904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999944968009454, \"rank\": 5.501235583142923e-06, \"text\": \"Christian values\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nihilists but not atheists as well?\", \"from\": 18907, \"to\": 18942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Convince me that \\\"the nihilists\\\" you are mentioning are not a different denomination of atheism; one whose article of faith is mocking deist religions.\", \"from\": 18944, \"to\": 19095, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never expressed criticism of the atheist religion if it is expressed in an academic sense (a poor descriptor I know) other than focusing on vilifying and mocking other religious faiths.\", \"from\": 19097, \"to\": 19289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As an agnostic, I rarely comment on atheists whose public statements  are confined to expressing their belief that there is no form of deity that other religions are based on.\", \"from\": 19291, \"to\": 19466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether the religion is an animistic religion, Abrahamic, Eastern, etc.\", \"from\": 19468, \"to\": 19539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Atheists like that are simply one more religious belief that I accept as just one more of the many religions that I do not accept for myself and remain agnostic.\", \"from\": 19541, \"to\": 19702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a confirmed atheist, you do not notice that atheists when publicly commenting predominantly focus on Christian religions to mock and condemn?\", \"from\": 19704, \"to\": 19848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19808, \"end\": 19817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9994084828430004, \"rank\": 0.0005918672565644208, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not notice it's rare that they ever pop up to mock Buddhism, Gaia, etc?\", \"from\": 19850, \"to\": 19928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not notice that they generally restrain themselves from mocking and condemning Judaism; and when they mock Judaism they ensure they throw Christianity into their comments as well?\", \"from\": 19930, \"to\": 20116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20016, \"end\": 20023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\", \"score\": 0.9999999998161684, \"rank\": 1.4283835270137396e-10, \"text\": \"Judaism\", \"types\": [], \"wi